data.description: WOW! You do NOT want to miss your chance to see this cozy cape cod in Coventry Local School District. Set back off the road with a paved driveway, this home features 2 bedrooms including a large master with a full bathroom as well. The kitchen comes stocked with all the appliances in excellent condition. This home has a newer roof, furnace, sump pump, and aeration tank. Complete with an addition on the back, partial basement, and central air conditioning, this home will NOT last! Call today to set up your own private showing before it's too late!
